title: JanSport Pack Review: Javelina
description: The JanSport Javelina is an adventure-ready pack featuring a hydration system or laptop pocket, top loading main compartment with internal divider and fully padded straps and back panel.

transcripts: Hey guys I'm Ahren back designer here at jansport and today I'm going to walk you through some awesome new product today we're going to talk about the Javelina part of our outside collection this is a 25 later pack that features 600 denier polyester as well as a synthetic leather trim on the back of the pack you'll notice the wedding hall handle as well as straight straps that are fully padded with a d-ring attachment point and a fully padded and quilted back panel on the side here we got a versatile pocket that's designed to hold a 15 inch laptop or a 3-liter hydration system each side has a water bottle pocket as well as compression straps the main compartment opens in a top-load orientation makes it really nice and easy to grab stuff out of there well it's sitting on the ground next to you it's also a nice little pocket here for notebooks or magazines in front of that you've got a tablet pocket that's zippered plush and added keep it nice and protected in front of that is a little pocket that will hold your brigalso has an organizer pocket put your cords pens your phone will fit in there dual daisy chains on the front as well as webbing loops so there you have the javelina as always guaranteed for life.
